title: Fuse Management Central: Systems' Alerts
agents: Fuse Management Central
catalog: opentextfuse
license: GPL
distribution: check_mk
description:
 This check monitors the systems' alerts from Fuse Management Central.
 If there are errors the check will return {CRIT}, if there are warnings without errors it will return {WARN}, otherwise {OK}.

inventory:
 One service is created for each pair system - component type.

item:
 The system type with the system name and the component type name.
